date.description: The date for which the data is recorded.

channel_id.description: The unique identifier of the YouTube channel.

video_id.description: The unique identifier of the video.

live_or_on_demand.description: Indicates whether the video is live or on demand.

subscribed_status.description: Indicates whether viewers were subscribed to the channel or not.

country_code.description: The country code associated with the data.

views.description: The total number of views on the channel.

comments.description: The total number of comments on the channel.

likes.description: The total number of likes on the channel.

dislikes.description: The total number of dislikes on the channel.

shares.description: The total number of shares of the channel's videos.

watch_time_minutes.description: The total watch time in minutes on the channel.

average_view_duration_seconds.description: The average duration in seconds that viewers watched a video.

average_view_duration_percentage.description: The average percentage of a video that viewers watched.

annotation_impressions.description: The total number of times annotations were shown to viewers.

annotation_clickable_impressions.description: The number of times viewers had the opportunity to click on annotations.

annotation_clicks.description: The total number of times viewers clicked on annotations.

annotation_click_through_rate.description: The percentage of times viewers clicked on annotations divided by the number of times annotations were shown.

annotation_closable_impressions.description: The number of times viewers had the opportunity to close annotations.

annotation_closes.description: The total number of times viewers closed annotations.

annotation_close_rate.description: The percentage of times viewers closed annotations divided by the number of times annotations were shown.

card_teaser_impressions.description: The total number of times card teasers were shown to viewers.

card_teaser_clicks.description: The total number of times viewers clicked on card teasers.

card_teaser_click_rate.description: The percentage of times viewers clicked on card teasers divided by the number of times teasers were shown.

card_impressions.description: The total number of times cards were shown to viewers.

card_clicks.description: The total number of times viewers clicked on cards.

card_click_rate.description: The percentage of times viewers clicked on cards divided by the number of times cards were shown.

subscribers_gained.description: The number of subscribers gained during the specified period.

subscribers_lost.description: The number of subscribers lost during the specified period.

videos_added_to_playlists.description: The total number of times videos were added to playlists.

videos_removed_from_playlists.description: The total number of times videos were removed from playlists.

red_views.description: The number of views coming from YouTube Red subscribers.

red_watch_time_minutes.description: The total amount of watch time in minutes from YouTube Red subscribers.
